| 1st   | +2 | _ | _ | _ | Unarmored Defense, Spectral Sight |
| 2nd   | +2 | 1d4 | _ | 1 | Illidari Initiation, Fel | 
| 3rd   | +2 | 1d4 | 1 | 2 | Demonic Mark, Demonic Mutations | 
| 4th   | +2 | 1d4 | 1 | 2 | Ability Score Improvement | 
| 5th   | +3 | 1d6 | 1 | 2 | Extra Attack, Demon's Bite | 
| 6th   | +3 | 1d6 | 1 | 2 | Metamorphosis | 
| 7th   | +3 | 1d6 | 1 | 3 | Evasion |
